  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A palm-sized orb of obsidian glass, the inside appearing like the night sky.</p><p>As an action, make a number of ranged attacks equal to half your proficiency, rounded up, at a creature within 60 feet as you fire small meteoric blasts.</p><p>On a hit, the creature takes 1d8 force damage and is knocked back 10ft.</p><p>Affected creatures must succeed a Strength save, with a -1 penalty for every attack they were hit with this tool, or fall prone.</p><p>The first attack made per turn, per creature, is unreactable.</p>",
